this is a java graphic engine(no audio code now)

run print exception about -Djava.library.path  please add the native library support . same that
toolbar->Run->Run Configurations...->java Application->Arguements->VM arguements 
-Djava.library.path="F:\.m2\repository\org\lwjgl\lwjgl\lwjgl-platform\2.9.3\lwjgl-platform-2.9.3-natives-windows"

my platform library path as the "F:\.m2\repository\org\lwjgl\lwjgl\lwjgl-platform\2.9.3\lwjgl-platform-2.9.3-natives-windows"

启动的时候会报错是因为没有指定本地依赖的动态库
在虚拟机运行配置选项里面的 加上
-Djava.library.path="F:\.m2\repository\org\lwjgl\lwjgl\lwjgl-platform\2.9.3\lwjgl-platform-2.9.3-natives-windows"

